                    <span>I thought I knew everything there was to know about HTML but was very shaky with style sheets and XML. This book takes you step by step through the learning process making XML and style sheets easy to understand by explaining why and how they are used. Recommend the book to anyone who is creating web sites! Every other HTML book pales in comparison.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Awesome Learning Aid</div>
